{"tid":2518473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蓋茨分身家 向妻子梅琳達轉讓近24億美元股份","createTime":"2021-05-06T05:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-06T05:37:29.000Z","uid":29620,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f3979c3188aea4e63db3fd06e0aa2e6e49f921fc","tid":2518473,"uid":29620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:02:01.000Z","msg":"華爾街日報》報道，微軟創辦人蓋茨(<a href=\"http://MSFT.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMSFT.US&d=lnSleIYCVJUMUgC9CFuHQobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=243ff48e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">MSFT.US</a>)  -1.320 (-0.533%)   已將旗下投資公司Cascade Investment總值近24億美元的股份轉讓予梅琳達，較早時兩人宣布離婚。<br />\n<br />\n截至周三收市，Cascade Investment向梅琳達轉讓墨西哥飲料公司Coca-Cola Femsa的所有4.9%股份，總值1.21億美元，以及墨西哥有線電視及廣播公司Grupo Televisa的全數6.7%股份，總市值3.86億美元。<br />\n<br />\n另外，Cascade Investment亦將約1.9%的加拿大國家鐵路公司(Canadian National Railway)股份以及約3.7%的AutoNation股份轉讓予梅琳達，兩者的股份市值約為15.5億及3.07億美元。"},{"pid":"79e62dd4ef14160e362a7ee41dea22cc4a7a7aee","tid":2518473,"uid":23445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:22:10.000Z","msg":"有錢毒撚都比人玩, 嗚嗚嗚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477dbdaa555b53a1662114ec3f51c8b2bdf37db1","tid":2518473,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:22:52.000Z","msg":"真係臭雞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0db82beb9c7a656d12c529066f59c1af14cef25","tid":2518473,"uid":165339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:26:25.000Z","msg":"有閪真係好尾機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0cddfe1e3f075539ecfb406a368a7781cbe8a51","tid":2518473,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:27:35.000Z","msg":"捐錢捐到咁盡"},{"pid":"5a0161cb0edf119034179a7e0638f4b024c5284b","tid":2518473,"uid":3302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"r